query:
INSERT INTO
            node_aggregation_witness_jobs_fri (
                l1_batch_number,
                circuit_id,
                depth,
                aggregations_url,
                number_of_dependent_jobs,
                protocol_version,
                status,
                created_at,
                updated_at,
                batch_created_at,
                protocol_version_patch
            )
            VALUES
            ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, 'waiting_for_proofs', NOW(), NOW(), $7, $8)
            ON CONFLICT (l1_batch_number, circuit_id, depth) DO
            UPDATE
            SET
            updated_at = NOW()
